{"tid":454300,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚萬聖節，點知中伏！","createTime":"2017-11-01T04:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T04:45:39.000Z","uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c90ea3b21be5778a1526afaa2001a2555ab1ea4","tid":454300,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，琴晚萬聖節就同一班姊妹落老蘭<br />\n佢哋一開頭就話要化得恐怖啲，嚇下班賤男<br />\n咁我就諗住扮喪屍bomber，因為都有人話過我似<br />\n去到見面嘅時候就知道仆街，陰鳩我！<br />\n個個都鬼火咁靚，又扮護士又扮惡魔又剩<br />\n屌你老母我係度就用黎顯得佢地幾靚<br />\n咁攻心計嘅朋友要唔要都罷<br />\n仆街喇八婆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e94483f1666aeb01b7879d2c93c664537cb89da","tid":454300,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"諗起舊登個籃球聚會<br />\n個個話自己廢<br />\n出到黎又甲組又乙組"},{"pid":"75c057690118240f8b75111e6f240b77e8687ed3","tid":454300,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"有圖未"},{"pid":"2e718ba70b63338c276a20f8ff7707d1d8337ef4","tid":454300,"uid":142029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"個po差啲野"},{"pid":"7e623857f82fb1fc6765fcde858d213126faf77f","tid":454300,"uid":38820,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/eFsKeuIrCM0z6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FeFsKeuIrCM0z6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c7da1d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e676ef728aee6e77ab08cd7b82a0efd0b57c90e","tid":454300,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"我嬲得濟 即刻走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff51149809730fd4373dc4589d618066d763e226","tid":454300,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:42:38.000Z","msg":